channel.title: Enclosures for sale
channel.description: I posted this in an existing topic but wanted to start a new one for those of you who might still be looking for an enclosure solution for your Axoloti Core. I've got a couple for sale below! I used the templates that janvantomme provided to produce an enclosure for my Axoloti. I added some different labeling and changed up the branding. I really liked the way it turned out. Thanks so much janvantomme for the files you provided. I had the room to make a couple of extra enclosures when I placed my order. I purchased enough hex bolts and nuts to make a couple of ready to assemble enclosure kits. You can buy them now on Ebay!
